00:04:06.930 --> 00:04:09.990 align:middle line:90%
it would require at least--

00:04:09.990 --> 00:04:12.240 align:middle line:84%
it would require all the
budgets to either be the same

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:12.990 align:middle line:90%
or increased.

00:04:12.990 --> 00:04:17.220 align:middle line:84%
But you can't-- and if you
